<!DOCTYPE html><html lang="en"><head><title>{{ $app->name_app }} - {{ $title }}</title><meta charset="utf-8"><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1"><meta name="description" content="{{ $app->name_app }} application documentation"><link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Open+Sans:300italic,400italic,600italic,700italic,800italic,400,300,600,700,800" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css"><script defer="defer" src="{{ asset('docs/assets/fontawesome/js/all.js') }}"></script><link rel="stylesheet" href="{{ asset('docs/assets/plugins/bootstrap/css/bootstrap.min.css') }}"><link rel="stylesheet" href="{{ asset('docs/assets/plugins/prism/prism.css') }}"><link rel="stylesheet" href="{{ asset('docs/assets/plugins/elegant_font/css/style.css') }}"><link rel="stylesheet" href="{{ asset('docs/assets/plugins/simplelightbox/simple-lightbox.min.css') }}"><link id="theme-style" rel="stylesheet" href="{{ asset('docs/assets/css/styles.css') }}"><link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Lobster&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"></head><body class="body-primary"><div class="page-wrapper"><header id="header" class="header"><div class="container"><div class="branding"><h1 class="logo"><a href="/"><i class="icon fa fa-trophy" style="color:#696cff"></i><span class="text-bold" style="font-family:Lobster,cursive;letter-spacing:1px;text-transform:none"> {{ $app->name_app }}</span></a></h1></div><ol class="breadcrumb"><li class="breadcrumb-item"><a href="/docs/v1">Home</a></li><li class="breadcrumb-item active">Documentation</li></ol></div></header><div class="doc-wrapper"><div class="container"><div id="doc-header" class="doc-header text-center"><h1 class="doc-title" style="font-weight:700"><span aria-hidden="true" class="icon_documents_alt icon"></span>&nbsp;Documentation</h1><div class="meta"><i class="far fa-clock"></i>&nbsp;Last updated: January 1, 2024</div></div><div class="doc-body row"><div class="doc-content col-md-9 col-12 order-1"><div class="content-inner"><section id="pendahuluan" class="doc-section"><h2 class="section-title">Introduction</h2><div class="section-block"><p>The introduction menu contains several important points such as registration tutorials and registration requirements.</p></div><div class="section-block" id="registrasi"><h4 class="block-title">How to register an account?</h4><p>Registering is actually quite easy. Besides manual registration, you can also register by contacting the admin directly. For manual registration, please follow these steps:</p><ol class="list"><li><b>First</b>, please visit the <a href="/register" target="_blank"><b>registration</b></a> link.</li><li><b>Second</b>, please fill out the available form. Enter your Full Name, username, email, Gender and password.</li><li><b>Third</b>, check the <b>'I agree to the terms & conditions'</b> box then click the <b>sign up</b> button.</li></ol><div class="callout-block callout-success" style="margin-top:20px;background-color:#696cff"><div class="content"><p><i class="fa-solid fa-bullhorn"></i><b> Tips:</b> Do not use your <i><b>name</b></i>, <i><b>username</b></i>, <i><b>birth date</b></i> or <i><b>email</b></i> as your password.</p></div></div></div></section><section id="materi" class="doc-section"><h2 class="section-title">Materials</h2><div class="section-block"><p>In the materials menu, users can view Javanese script learning materials including various Javanese letters, sandhangan (diacritics), and their pairs, as well as listen to pronunciation audio.</p></div><div id="akses-materi" class="section-block"><h4 class="block-title">How to view materials?</h4><p>To view materials, please visit this <a href="/materi" target="_blank"><b>link</b></a>.</p><p><img class="img-responsive w-75 border border-primary" src="{{ asset('docs/assets/img/materi.png') }}" alt="how to access materials {{ $app->name_app }}"></p></div><div id="voice" class="section-block"><h4 class="block-title">How to access voice materials?</h4><p>To access voice materials, please visit the materials menu through this <a href="/materi" target="_blank"><b>link</b></a>. After that, you can click on one of the Javanese script letters. With these steps, the voice will automatically play for you.</p><p><img class="img-responsive w-75 border border-primary" src="{{ asset('docs/assets/img/voice-materi.png') }}" alt="how to access voice materials {{ $app->name_app }}"></p></div></section><section id="quiz" class="doc-section"><h2 class="section-title">Quiz</h2><div class="section-block"><p>The 'Quiz' menu contains questions that can be answered to practice understanding of Javanese script. These quizzes can be taken repeatedly.</p></div><div id="akses-quiz" class="section-block"><h4 class="block-title">How to access quizzes?</h4><p>To access quizzes, please visit this <a href="/quiz" target="_blank"><b>link</b></a>.</p><p><img class="img-responsive w-75 border border-primary" src="{{ asset('docs/assets/img/akses-quiz.png') }}" alt="how to access quizzes {{ $app->name_app }}"></p></div><div id="detail-quiz" class="section-block"><h4 class="block-title">How to view quiz details?</h4><p>To view quiz details, you can look for the small icon in the top right corner of the quiz.</p><p><img class="img-responsive w-75 border border-primary" src="{{ asset('docs/assets/img/detail-quiz.png') }}" alt="how to view quiz details {{ $app->name_app }}"></p></div><div id="akses-soal" class="section-block"><h4 class="block-title">How to take a quiz?</h4><p>To take a quiz, please visit the quiz menu first through this <a href="/quiz" target="_blank"><b>link</b></a>. You can press one of the <b>"Start Quiz"</b> buttons. To finish the quiz, you can press the <b>"Finish"</b> button then click <b>"Send"</b>.</p><p><img class="img-responsive w-75 border border-primary" src="{{ asset('docs/assets/img/akses-soal.png') }}" alt="how to take quiz questions {{ $app->name_app }}"></p></div><div id="akses-nilai-quiz" class="section-block"><h4 class="block-title">How to access quiz scores?</h4><p>To access quiz scores, please visit the scores menu through this <a href="/nilai" target="_blank"><b>link</b></a>. You can also view quiz scores after completing quiz questions.</p><p><img class="img-responsive w-75 border border-primary" src="{{ asset('docs/assets/img/nilai-quiz.png') }}" alt="how to access quiz scores {{ $app->name_app }}"></p></div></section><section id="forum" class="doc-section"><h2 class="section-title">Forum</h2><div class="section-block"><p>The forum is used for discussion if there are problems regarding the available materials. Each user can ask questions and these questions can be answered by other users through comments.</p></div><div id="add-thread" class="section-block"><h4 class="block-title">How to add a thread?</h4><p>To add a thread, please visit this <a href="/view/discuss" target="_blank"><b>link</b></a>. After that, click the <b>Add Thread</b> button. Wait until the popup box appears. Finally enter the thread <b>title</b> and <b>description</b> then press the <b>"Send"</b> button.</p><p><img class="img-responsive w-75 border border-primary" src="{{ asset('docs/assets/img/tambah-thread.png') }}" alt="how to add thread {{ $app->name_app }}"></p></div><div id="delete-thread" class="section-block"><h4 class="block-title">How to delete a thread?</h4><p>To delete a thread, you can look for the small icon in the top right corner of the thread. Press it then select the <b>'Delete'</b> option. Wait until the confirmation popup appears. After that, you can click the <b>'Yes, Delete!'</b> button.</p><p><img class="img-responsive w-75 border border-primary" src="{{ asset('docs/assets/img/delete-thread.png') }}" alt="how to delete thread {{ $app->name_app }}"></p><p><img class="img-responsive w-75 border border-primary" src="{{ asset('docs/assets/img/confirm-delete.png') }}" alt="delete thread popup {{ $app->name_app }}"></p></div><div id="add-comment" class="section-block"><h4 class="block-title">How to add a thread comment?</h4><p>To add a comment to a thread, please visit the thread menu first through this <a href="/view/discuss" target="_blank"><b>link</b></a>. You can choose one of the threads you want to comment on. Enter your comment in the provided form. You can also reply to other people's comments.</p><p><img class="img-responsive w-75 border border-primary" src="{{ asset('docs/assets/img/add-comment.png') }}" alt="how to add thread comment {{ $app->name_app }}"></p></div><div id="delete-comment" class="section-block"><h4 class="block-title">How to delete a thread comment?</h4><p>To delete a thread comment, you can press the <b>delete</b> button on the comment you want to delete. Then wait until the confirmation popup appears, then click <b>'Yes, Delete!'</b>.</p><p><img class="img-responsive w-75 border border-primary" src="{{ asset('docs/assets/img/delete-comment.png') }}" alt="how to delete thread comment {{ $app->name_app }}"></p></div><div id="user-like" class="section-block"><h4 class="block-title">How to see who liked my thread?</h4><p>To see the total and who liked my thread, you can click on one of your threads. After that, click the <b>'heart'</b> icon next to the share icon in the top right corner.</p><p><img class="img-responsive w-75 border border-primary" src="{{ asset('docs/assets/img/who-like.png') }}" alt="how to see who liked my thread {{ $app->name_app }}"></p></div><div id="like-thread" class="section-block"><h4 class="block-title">How to like a thread?</h4><p>To like a thread, you can click the 'heart' icon on one of your threads. After that, click the <b>'heart'</b> icon next to the comment icon on the thread. Wait until the color changes to red.</p><p><img class="img-responsive w-75 border border-primary" src="{{ asset('docs/assets/img/like-thread.png') }}" alt="how to like a thread {{ $app->name_app }}"></p></div></section><section id="pengaturan" class="doc-section"><h2 class="section-title">Settings</h2><div class="section-block"><p>In settings, users can view and change personal identity such as name, address, profile photo etc. Users can also change their password.</p></div><div id="change-email" class="section-block"><h4 class="block-title">How to change account email?</h4><p>To change email, please visit settings or through this <a href="/pengaturan" target="_blank"><b>link</b></a>. After that, click the <b>'pencil'</b> icon. Wait until the popup box appears. Enter your password for verification. Finally, enter the <b>new email</b> then click the <b>'Save'</b> button.</p><p><img class="img-responsive w-75 border border-primary" src="{{ asset('docs/assets/img/change-email.png') }}" alt="how to change email {{ $app->name_app }}"></p></div><div id="change-username" class="section-block"><h4 class="block-title">How to change account username?</h4><p>To change username, please visit <a href="/pengaturan" target="_blank"><b>settings</b></a>. Enter username in the provided input form, then click the <b>'Save'</b> button.</p><p><img class="img-responsive w-75 border border-primary" src="{{ asset('docs/assets/img/change-username.png') }}" alt="how to change username {{ $app->name_app }}"></p></div><div id="change-password" class="section-block"><h4 class="block-title">How to change account password?</h4><p>To change password, please visit <a href="/pengaturan" target="_blank"><b>settings</b></a>. After that, click the <b>'Account'</b> tab. Enter your old password, then enter the new password and confirm password. Finally, click the <b>'Save'</b> button. If you forgot your old password, you can contact the admin to reset your password.</p><p><img class="img-responsive w-75 border border-primary" src="{{ asset('docs/assets/img/change-password.png') }}" alt="how to change password {{ $app->name_app }}"></p></div><div class="callout-block callout-success" style="margin-top:20px;background-color:#696cff"><div class="content"><p><i class="fa-solid fa-bullhorn"></i><b> Tips:</b> Do not use your <i><b>name</b></i>, <i><b>username</b></i>, <i><b>birth date</b></i> or <i><b>email</b></i> as your password.</p></div></div></section></div></div><div class="doc-sidebar col-md-3 col-12 order-0 d-none d-md-flex"><div id="doc-nav" class="doc-nav"><nav id="doc-menu" class="nav doc-menu flex-column sticky"><li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link scrollto" href="#pendahuluan">Introduction</a></li><nav class="nav doc-sub-menu nav flex-column"><li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link scrollto" href="#registrasi">Registration</a></li></nav><li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link scrollto" href="#materi">Materials</a></li><nav class="nav doc-sub-menu nav flex-column"><li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link scrollto" href="#akses-materi">View Materials</a></li><li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link scrollto" href="#voice">Access Voice Materials</a></li></nav><li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link scrollto" href="#quiz">Quiz</a></li><nav class="nav doc-sub-menu nav flex-column"><li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link scrollto" href="#akses-quiz">Access Quiz</a></li><li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link scrollto" href="#detail-quiz">View Quiz Details</a></li><li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link scrollto" href="#akses-soal">Take Quiz</a></li><li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link scrollto" href="#akses-nilai-quiz">Access Quiz Scores</a></li></nav><li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link scrollto" href="#forum">Forum</a></li><nav class="nav doc-sub-menu nav flex-column"><li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link scrollto" href="#add-thread">Add Thread</a></li><li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link scrollto" href="#delete-thread">Delete Thread</a></li><li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link scrollto" href="#add-comment">Add Comments</a></li><li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link scrollto" href="#delete-comment">Delete Comments</a></li><li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link scrollto" href="#user-like">Who Liked My Threads?</a></li><li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link scrollto" href="#like-thread">Like Threads</a></li></nav><li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link scrollto" href="#pengaturan">Settings</a></li><nav class="nav doc-sub-menu nav flex-column"><li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link scrollto" href="#change-email">Change Account Email</a></li><li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link scrollto" href="#change-username">Change Account Username</a></li><li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link scrollto" href="#change-password">Change Account Password</a></li></nav></nav></div></div></div></div></div><div id="promo-block" class="promo-block" style="background-color:#696cff"><div class="container"><div class="promo-block-inner"><h3 id="about" class="promo-title text-center"><p><em class="fa fa-trophy text-white"></em> About {{ $app->name_app }}</p></h3><div class="row"><div class="figure-holder col-md-5 col-sm-12 col-xs-12"><div class="figure-holder-inner"><a href="" target="_blank"><img class="img-responsive w-100" src="{{ asset('docs/assets/img/bubblesmart.png') }}" alt="{{ $app->name_app }}"></a><a class="mask" href="/"><i class="icon fa fa-trophy" style="color:#696cff"></i></a></div></div><div class="content-holder col-md-7 col-xs-12"><div class="content-holder-inner"><div class="desc"><h4 class="content-title"><p><strong>What is&nbsp;{{ $app->name_app }}&nbsp;?</strong></p></h4><p>{{ $app->description_app }}</p><h4 class="content-title"><p><strong>How to use&nbsp;{{ $app->name_app }}&nbsp;?</strong></p></h4><p>Using this application is quite easy, first, you can register directly through this <a href="/register" class="text-white" style="text-decoration:none"><i><b>link</b></i></a>. After registering, you can access all user features available in the&nbsp;{{ $app->name_app }} application</p><p class="author">Author:&nbsp;<a href="http://github.com/polzNautica" target="_blank" class="text-white" style="text-decoration:none">@Bubble</a></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><footer id="footer" class="footer text-center"><div class="container"><small class="copyright">Copyright&nbsp;<script>document.write((new Date).getFullYear())</script>&nbsp;<a href="/" class="text-decoration-none"><b>{{ $app->name_app }}</b>.</a>&nbsp;All rights reserved</small></div></footer><script src="{{ asset('docs/assets/plugins/bootstrap/js/bootstrap.min.js') }}"></script><script src="{{ asset('docs/assets/plugins/prism/prism.js') }}"></script><script src="{{ asset('docs/assets/plugins/stickyfill/dist/stickyfill.min.js') }}"></script><script src="{{ asset('docs/assets/plugins/gumshoe/gumshoe.polyfills.min.js') }}"></script><script src="{{ asset('docs/assets/plugins/simplelightbox/simple-lightbox.min.js') }}"></script><script src="{{ asset('docs/assets/js/main.js') }}"></script></body></html>